    <!-- 手作坊-旧物再利用制作视频详情页 -->
    <section id="reuse-video-details" class="page-section py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
          <a href="#workshop" class="text-primary mr-4">
            <i class="fa fa-arrow-left text-xl"></i>
          </a>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary">
            <i class="fa fa-video-camera mr-3"></i>旧物再利用制作视频
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-8">
          <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 mb-6">
            <div class="w-full h-96 bg-gray-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <i class="fa fa-play-circle text-6xl text-primary mb-4"></i>
                <p class="text-gray-500">点击播放视频</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mb-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">旧衣物变宠物玩具制作教程</h3>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-gray-500">
                <span><i class="fa fa-calendar mr-1"></i> 2023-11-15</span>
                <span><i class="fa fa-eye mr-1"></i> 1.2k 次观看</span>
                <span><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up mr-1"></i> 89</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
              <button class="inline-block px-6 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-medium hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                <i class="fa fa-heart mr-2"></i>收藏视频
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">视频简介</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              本视频教程将教您如何将家中闲置的旧衣物改造成可爱又实用的宠物玩具。通过简单的手工制作，不仅可以减少浪费，还能为校园里的流浪动物提供温暖的陪伴。
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              制作过程简单易学，所需材料也很常见，适合所有手工爱好者参与。让我们一起用双手为流浪动物创造更多的爱与关怀吧！
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">制作步骤</h3>
              
              <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
                    1
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">准备材料</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      收集所需材料：旧衣物（最好是柔软的棉织物）、剪刀、针线、棉花或填充物、纽扣或其他装饰材料。
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">必备材料</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>旧衣物2-3件</li>
                          <li>剪刀</li>
                          <li>针线</li>
                          <li>棉花或填充物</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">可选材料</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>纽扣</li>
                          <li>丝带</li>
                          <li>铃铛</li>
                          <li>彩色线</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
                    2
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">裁剪布料</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      将旧衣物平铺，根据设计图案裁剪出所需的布料形状。本教程以制作一个简单的骨头形状玩具为例，您可以根据自己的创意设计不同的形状。
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">裁剪尺寸</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>骨头形状：长20cm，宽8cm</li>
                          <li>需要裁剪2片相同形状的布料</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">裁剪技巧</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>使用锋利的剪刀</li>
                          <li>布料要铺平，避免褶皱</li>
                          <li>可以先用笔画出轮廓再裁剪</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
                    3
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">缝制玩具</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      将裁剪好的两片布料正面相对，用针线沿着边缘缝合，注意要留出一个小口子用于填充棉花。
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">缝制方法</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>使用平针缝或回针缝</li>
                          <li>缝边宽度约0.5cm</li>
                          <li>留出约3cm的开口</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">注意事项</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>针线要牢固</li>
                          <li>边角处要仔细缝制</li>
                          <li>不要将开口缝死</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
                    4
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">填充棉花</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      通过预留的开口将棉花填充到玩具内部，填充的松紧程度可以根据个人喜好调整。填充完成后，用针线将开口缝好。
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">填充技巧</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>使用小工具（如筷子）帮助填充</li>
                          <li>边角处也要填充饱满</li>
                          <li>不要填充过满，避免布料破裂</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">安全提示</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>确保棉花干净卫生</li>
                          <li>填充过程中注意安全</li>
                          <li>缝口要牢固，防止棉花溢出</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
                    5
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">装饰完成</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      根据个人创意，为制作好的宠物玩具添加装饰，如缝上纽扣做眼睛、用丝带系蝴蝶结等。
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">装饰方法</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>缝上纽扣做眼睛</li>
                          <li>用丝带系蝴蝶结</li>
                          <li>添加铃铛增加趣味性</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">创意建议</h5>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                          <li>可以制作不同形状的玩具</li>
                          <li>使用不同颜色的布料</li>
                          <li>为玩具起个可爱的名字</li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
