              <!-- 分享2：救助经历 -->
              <div class="bg-secondary/5 rounded-xl p-4 card-shadow hover:bg-secondary/10 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-3">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1012/100/100" alt="用户头像" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">李同学</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">昨天</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <a href="share_detail.html" class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2 hover:underline">分享一次成功的流浪动物救助经历</a>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                  上周三，我在图书馆后面发现一只受伤的小奶猫，它的后腿好像被什么东西夹过，无法正常行走。我立即联系了救助站的老师，我们一起将小猫送到了医院进行治疗。经过医生的精心治疗，小猫的伤势已经稳定，现在正在康复中...
                </p>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-500">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <button class="flex items-center text-gray-500 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                      <i class="fa fa-thumbs-up mr-1"></i>
                      <span>32</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex items-center text-gray-500 hover:text-primary transition-colors ml-4">
                      <i class="fa fa-comment mr-1"></i>
                      <span>12</span>
                    </button>
                  </div>
                  <span class="inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/5 text-primary text-xs font-medium">
                    救助经历
                  </span>
